These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, skydiving, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | dancing  | writing | skydiving | magic-tricks  |
| Sport   | sailing | skateboarding   | baseball  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, papaya, artichoke, cherry
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, police-officer, analyst, dancer
1. the dancer is not to the left of the dancer##8
2. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
3. the person eating apple is the police-officer##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the person eating apple and the person eating papaya##2
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the freelancer##7
6. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
7. the freelancer is not to the left of the freelancer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | artichoke | papaya          | cherry | apple     |
| Job    | analyst      | dancer | freelancer | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, teacher, manager, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, drama, scientific, time-travel
1. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the manager##8
2. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
3. the teacher is on the right of the musician##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4
5. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
6. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
7. the doctor is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | musician | teacher | manager     | doctor |
| Movie-Genre   | drama    | time-travel   | thriller | scientific    |

