.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, hip-hop, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, skiing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
5. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | classical         | electronic   | gospel    |
| Sport         | volleyball | rowing | skiing | snowboarding |

