.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, horror, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, weightlifting, skateboarding
1. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
2. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
3. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching comedy movies##7
4. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who's sport is skiing##7
6. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | horror | action | comedy    |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding   | weightlifting   | skiing |

