3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the fan of country##8
7. the person eating strawberry is the fan of country##1

