.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, fanta, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, parkour, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is parkour##7
3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
6. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | fanta | juice | coffee   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | parkour | biathlon  | sailing |

