.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, funk, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, helicopter, subway
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of d&b and the person driving the car##2
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
4. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
5. the person driving the tram is the person driving the tram##1
6. the fan of funk is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the fan of d&b is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
8. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | disco | funk | house |
| Transport     | subway | tram       | car  | helicopter    |

