.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, peas, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, chess, woodworking, dancing
1. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating peas is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | grapefruit        | orange | peas      | artichoke    |
| Hobby   | cooking | woodworking   | chess | dancing |

