.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, rugby, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate         | lemonade    | iced-tea       |
| Sport      | golf | cycling | surfing | rugby |

