3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
4. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | milk     | coffee | hot-chocolate        | juice       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | baking  | traveling | puzzles |

