.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, onion, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, spy, western, martial-arts
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 2. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 3. the person eating mango is the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating mango is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
 9. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
10. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | peach    | onion | mango | radish |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | martial-arts  | western     | spy    |

