2. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating zucchini##2
7. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4

