.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, ferret, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, bus, roller
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person driving the bus##6
2. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
4. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
6. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
7. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | guinea-pig | rat  | ferret  |
| Transport   | taxi | skateboard   | roller | bus |

