.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, guinea-pig, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, skateboard, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the bus##1
5. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the bus##7
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the tram and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | lizard    | dog | mouse | guinea-pig |
| Transport   | helicopter | tram      | skateboard     | bus     |

 